25-year-old man, Ghaddafi Saleh, was found dead inside the main gutter at Tarauni Zaria Road by Veterinary Hospital in Kano State. This was confirmed in a statement issued by Alhaji Saminu Abdullahi, the Public Relations Officer of Kano State Fire Service, on Wednesday in Kano. His body was found after the fire service received an emergency call at about 7am from one Malam Abdulkadir. “We immediately sent our rescue team to the scene at about 7:34a.m. “The victim was, however, brought out of the gutter unconscious and later confirmed dead.” The PRO added that the deceased corpse was handed over to Insp. Bashir Abdullahi of Zaria Road Police Division. Abdullahi mentioned the cause of the incident was the heavy rainfall of last Sunday.